      "versionDate": "2026-02-27",
      "versionDescription": "> [!Warning]\r\n> The standalone version requires SideStore 0.6.2+ or AltStore 2.2.1+ for installation.\r\n> To install LiveContainer with built-in SideStore (LiveContainer+SideStore.ipa), please use [Impactor](https://github.com/khcrysalis/Impactor) or [iloader](https://github.com/nab138/iloader). See [our installation guide](https://livecontainer.github.io/docs/installation/lc_sidestore) for details.\r \n>[!Note]\r\n> This a minor release that solves the following issues in version 3.7.0 and adds the following features. For more information, please see [3.7.0 release note](https://github.com/LiveContainer/LiveContainer/releases/tag/3.7.0).\r \nBug Fixes\r \n• Fix an issue where built-in SideStore may freeze on launch (1158)\r\n• Fix the ipa of another LiveContainer not generating in LiveContainer+SideStore builds after SideStore's massive codebase change (1184)\r\n• Fix the new Launch App Shortcut does not work below iOS 18 (1159)\r\n• The Launch App Shortcut now reports meaningful errors\r\n• Fix crash when using external container in multitasking mode\r\n• Fix process hangs when debugging multitask private apps\r \nNew Features\r\n• The \"Tap top of the view to scroll to top\" action can be passed through to multitasking guest apps.",
      "downloadURL": "https://github.com/LiveContainer/LiveContainer/releases/download/3.7.2/LiveContainer%2BSideStore.ipa",
